-- Lima Exchange Expects 20 Listings of Miners, Lenders and Industry in 2010
-- Alex Emery
-- 2010-06-24T20:03:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/lima-exchange-expects-20-listings-of-miners-lenders-and-industry-in-2010.html

          
          
             The Lima Stock Exchange expects 20
companies to list shares this year as part of a drive to raise
financing for investment projects, general manager Francis
Stenning said today.  
 Listings may include savings and loan institutions, miners
and industrial companies, Stenning said in an interview at the
Lima Stock Exchange.  
